author: Kruggsmash
description:
*An edited, illustrated and narrated playthrough of the game Dwarf Fortress*

 Welcome back to Dwarf Fortress, my good bearded bastards! It looks like theres been a big update to the game that will add a lot more siege-related challenges to fortress life. But of course, there's also a great many new ways to defend ourselves as well! Today we're going to dip our toes in, see the new weaponry and get a brief look at what this update has to offer (despite me being the stupidest bastard to ever strike the earth..you'll see.)

Music by Ivan Duch: https://ivanduch.com/

Intro & End tunes by Topher Anselmo: https://topheranselmo.com/

Illustration Coloring by Mrs K

https://www.patreon.com/c/Kruggsmash
title: Short Forts: Failedplans, Siege Update First Looks
